{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUser:emails:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUser:emails:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setUser:emails:","role":"symbol"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user identifier and emails together in a single operation."}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"userId"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"emails:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"userId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"emails","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Array of email address strings to associate with the user.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Convenience method that combines "},{"code":"setUserId:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setEmails:"},{"type":"text","text":" into a single"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"server request. This is more efficient than calling both methods separately"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and ensures atomic association of user ID with emails.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this during login or registration flows when you have both user ID"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and email available simultaneously."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Complete registration with user ID and emails:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class RegistrationManager {","","    func completeRegistration(_ registration: RegistrationData) {","        \/\/ Create user on backend","        APIClient.shared.createUser(registration) { result in","            guard case .success(let user) = result else { return }","","            \/\/ Set both user ID and emails in single operation","            var emails = [user.email]","            if let secondaryEmail = registration.secondaryEmail {","                emails.append(secondaryEmail)","            }","","            Pushwoosh.configure.setUser(user.id, emails: emails)","","            \/\/ Set initial user tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"registration_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                \"registration_source\": registration.source.rawValue,","                \"account_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","                \"has_completed_onboarding\": false","            ])","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["   when you need confirmation."]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUser:emails:":{"role":"symbol","title":"setUser:emails:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets user identifier and emails together in a single operation.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"abstract":[],"role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"}}}